Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
The Tyler Village mixed-use complex sits in the heart of Cleveland’s St. Clair-Superior neighborhood. This dynamic area is home to iconic landmark hot spots (Slyman’s Deli), the “Pho Row” groups of restaurants, galleries, grocery and Asian food markets. Offering close proximity to Interstate I-90, Route 2, University
Circle and Downtown Cleveland, Tyler Village’s convenient location is a leading factor in the neighborhoods growth.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Tyler Village offers an exceptional environment for businesses to thrive. Building 44’s large, efficient floor plates, ample natural light, collaborative meeting areas and open, exposed ceilings are ideal for the modern office. Meanwhile, Buildings 20 and 41 offer a warehouse office environment along with accessible maker space, perfect for growing entrepreneurial companies, non-profits and shops. The Tyler Village campus also provides businesses with a host of other conveniences with on-site café, outdoor gathering spaces, building conference rooms, covered and open parking options, along with on-site management.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Tyler Village in the heart of Cleveland's St. Clair-Superior neighborhood
